            <title>[CASSANDRA-19350] Add cli log level to circle config</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-19350</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We try to set the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/.circleci/config_template.yml#L3538&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;log cli level&lt;/a&gt; so that dtest logging is captured to stdout, but we don&apos;t do it &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/.circleci/config_template.yml#L3063&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;everywhere&lt;/a&gt; so we miss some logs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
